Tirada kiisaska COVID-19 ee soo kordhay ee ka dhacay Midowga Yurub / Aagga Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Midowday laga bilaabo 1 Janaayo ilaa 15 Maarso 2020
Kiisaska sii kordhaya ee cudurka Coronavirus (COVID-19) waxay muujiyaan isbarbardhigyo isku mid ah oo ka dhexeeya waddamada Midowga Yurub / Aagga Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Midowday taas oo xaqiijineysa in COVID-19 uu si dhakhso leh u socdo dhammaan wadamada, in kasta oo heerarka kala duwan ay ku kala duwan yihiin wadamada.
Iyada oo ku saleysan aqoonta laga helay Talyaaniga, wadamada, isbitaalada iyo cutubyada daryeelka xoogga leh ee COVID-19 ayaa loo baahan yahay inay sii diyaariyaan kororka degdegga ah ee bukaannada u baahan daryeel caafimaad oo gaar ahaan daryeel degdeg ah.
31 December 2019 waxaa lagu soo warramay in uu ka dhacay magaalada Wuhan ee gobolka Hubei ee dalka Shiinaha kiisaska cudurka 'Pneumonia' ee la xiriira aragtida aan la aqoon ee cudurka.
9ka Janaayo 2020, Xarunta Xakamaynta iyo Kahortagga Cudurrada ee Shiinaha ayaa sheegtay in coronavirus-ka cusub uu hadda loo tixgeliyo sida coronavirus-ka neefsashada daran ee daran ee 2 (SARS-CoV-2) oo ah qayb wax ku ool ah.
Sidaa darteed, cudurka ka dhashay cudurka SARS-CoV-2 ayaa loo magacaabay cudurka Coronavirus (COVID-19).
Xogta xaqiiqada ah ee la helay ilaa hadda waa in 80% dadka qaba COVID-19 ay qabaan cudur fudud, taas oo ah cudurrada neefta ee neefta ama aan lahayn, inta badanna ay ka bogsadaan.
14% dadka qaba COVID-19 waxay u muuqdaan inay noqdaan cudur aad u daran oo u baahan in la isbitaalo, halka 6% ay qabaan cudur aad u daran oo u baahan daryeel degdeg ah.
Tirada dhimashada ee bukaanka la cusbitaaliyo ee COVID-19 waxay qiyaastii tahay 4%.
Sahankan waxaan ku falanqeyneynaa isbeddellada COVID-19 ee ku soo kordha waddan kasta oo ka tirsan Midowga Yurub / Aagga Dhaqaalaha Yurub (EU/EEA) iyo Boqortooyada Ingiriiska (UK) oo aan isbarbardhigno gobolka Xubey ee Shiinaha.
Waxaan sidoo kale isbarbardhignaa tirada hadda jira ee COVID-19 ee dalalka EU/EEA iyo UK tirada Talyaaniga inta u dhexeysa 31 Janaayo - 15 Maarso 2020.
Xaaladaha COVID-19 ee dalalka EU / EEA iyo Boqortooyada Midowday
Shiinaha ayaa ka dambeeya COVID-19 oo si ballaaran u faafay, waxaana hadda dalkaasi ku soo socda dhaqdhaqaaqa cudurka faafa ee COVID-19 ee adduunka intiisa kale.
Agaasimaha Guud ee Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO) ayaa COVID-19 ku dhawaaqay cudur faafa 11 -kii Maarso 2020.
Marka la eego tirada 5da Maarso ee Eurosaurveillance 2020, Spiteri iyo asxaabteeda ayaa soo sheegay in ay yihiin dadka ugu horreeya ee Yurub ee xaqiijiyay kiisaska COVID-19 sida lagu qeexay kiisaska WHO.
EU/EEA, Faransiiska ayaa 24ka Janaayo 2020 sheegay in saddexda kiis ee ugu horreeya ee la xaqiijiyay ay ka soo noqdeen Wuhan, gobolka Hubei ee Shiinaha.
Ilaa 15ka Maarso 2020, dhammaan 30 waddan oo ka mid ah EU/EEA iyo Boqortooyada Ingiriiska ayaa la helay COVID-19, iyadoo laga soo xigtay 31kii Diseembar 2019 ilaa taariikhda la sheegay, 39,768 kiis iyo 1,727 dhimashada, iyadoo 17,750 kiis iyo 1,441 dhimashada ay ka dhaceen Talyaaniga oo keliya.
Tirada iyo baaxadda COVID-19 ee la helay
Xarunta Yurub ee Ka Hortagga iyo Xakamaynta Cudurrada (ECDC) waxay soo bandhigtaa tirada COVID-19 ee laga helay waddan kasta oo adduunka ah oo laga helo ilo dawladeed oo kaliya sida Wasaaradaha Caafimaadka, Hay'adaha Caafimaadka Qaranka iyo Goboleedyada iyo WHO, oo la cusbooneysiiyo maalin kasta 8:00 subaxnimo.
Macluumaadkan waxaa loo isticmaalay in lagu qiimeeyo isbeddellada COVID-19 ee EU/EEA iyo UK iyo in la barbardhigo wixii ka dhacay Talyaaniga.
Marka loo eego kiisaska COVID-19 ee firfircoon, waxaan xisaabinay 14 maalmood oo kor u kaca COVID-19, taas oo tixgelineysa socdaalka dabiiciga ah ee COVID-19 ee 1da Janaayo - 15 Maarso 2020 ee waddan kasta oo ka mid ah EU/EEA iyo Boqortooyada Midowday.
Waxaan sidoo kale soo bandhignay tirada diiwaangashan ee kiisaska diiwaangashan ee dal kasta ilaa 8:00 subaxnimo ee 15 -ka Maarso 2020 marka la barbar dhigo kiisaska Talyaaniga ee muddada 31 -ka Janaayo - 15 -ka Maarso 2020.
Isbeddellada COVID-19 ee dalalka EU / EEA iyo Boqortooyada Midowday
14 maalmood oo gaaban oo COVID-19 ah oo ku kordhay wadamada EU/EEA iyo Boqortooyada Midowday ayaa caadi ahaan la raacay xaaladda gobolka Hubei (Shiinaha) (Sawir 1).
EU/EEA iyo guud ahaan Boqortooyada Midowday, kiisaska COVID-19 ee la isku daray waxay bilaabeen inay kor u kacaan 21ka Febraayo, ka dibna waxay si kulul u kordheen 28ka Febraayo 2020 (waxyaabo dheeri ah).
Tani waxay si weyn ugu horseeday kororka degdegga ah ee tirada kiisaska la soo sheegay ee Talyaaniga, laakiin dhammaan waddamada kale ee EU/EEA iyo Boqortooyada Midowday waxay muujiyeen isbeddel isku mid ah kororka kiisaska COVID-19 ee kor u kaca (wax soo saarka).
Sawirka 2 wuxuu muujinayaa isbarbardhigga tirada Talyaaniga ee kiisaska COVID-19 ee ku soo kordha wadamada EU/EEA iyo Boqortooyada Midowday intii u dhaxaysay 31 Janaayo-15 Maarso 2020.
Waxaa xusid mudan in ilaa 8:00 subaxnimo ee Maarso 15, 15 dal oo kale oo ka tirsan Midowga Yurub/Madaxweynaha Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Midowday ay soo sheegeen tirada kiisaska guud ee la barbar dhigo Talyaaniga oo kaliya 3 toddobaad ka hor ama ka yar.
Natiijooyinkayagu waxay tilmaamayaan in tirada kiisaska COVID-19 ee la yaqaan ay si degdeg ah ugu sii kordhayaan EU/EEA iyo Boqortooyada Midowday.
Isbeddellada la arkay ee kiisaska COVID-19 ee sii kordhaya waxay tilmaamayaan in masiibada ay ku socotay xawaare isbarbardhig ah wadamada oo dhan.
Tani waa in la ogaado in ay jiraan heerar kala duwan oo ay wadamada ku jiraan, iyadoo ay jiraan kala duwanaansho ka jira jawaabaha caafimaadka dadweynaha ee qaranka, iyo in ay jiraan qeexitaanno kala duwan oo laga yaabo in lagu helo dadka qaba cudurka iyo borotokoolyo kala duwan oo lagu kala saaro dadka buka oo ay tahay in la tijaabiyo COVID-19, oo ay ku jiraan baaritaanka qabashada.
Bilowgii Maarso 2020, dhakhaatiir ku sugan gobollada ay ku jirto cudurka COVID-19 ee Talyaaniga ayaa tilmaamay xaalad ay u baahan yihiin daryeel degdeg ah 10% bukaanka qaba COVID-19 iyo warbaahinta ayaa sheegtay in isbitaalada iyo cutubyada daryeelka degdegga ah ee gobolladaasi ay horeyba u gaareen awoodooda ugu badan.
Xogta ku saabsan gelitaanka COVID-19 ee isbitaalka iyo / ama cutubka daryeelka xoogga leh ayaa hadda laga heli karaa heerarka EU / EEA oo kaliya 6% iyo 1% oo kiisaska ah (macluumaadka lama muujiyo).
Si kastaba ha noqotee, waa in si nidaamsan loo ururiyaa si loo buuxiyo xogta kormeerka ee hadda jirta oo diiradda saaraya tirada kiisaska la soo sheegay iyo tirada dhimashada.
Daraasad lagu sameeyay 2010-11 oo lagu sameeyay qiyaastii 29.2 sariirood oo 100,000 oo qof oo ku nool Jarmalka ilaa Portugal ayaa muujisay farqi weyn oo u dhexeeya helitaanka daryeelka xoogga iyo sariirta daryeelka dhexdhexaadka ah ee Yurub.
Taas macnaheedu waa in wadamada ay ka heli karaan ilo ka yar ama ka badan Talyaaniga (in 201011 12.5 sariiro daryeel degdeg ah iyo daryeel dhexdhexaad ah oo 100,000 qof).
Marka la eego heerarka guud ee kiisaska COVID-19 ee isbitaalka laga soo galo waddan kasta oo EU/EEA ah iyo Boqortooyada Midowday, xaaladaha lagu daydo ee ku saabsan ku-darka awoodda daryeelka caafimaadka waxay muujinayaan in halis > 90% ah oo ah in lagu xadido awoodda sariiraha daryeelka degdegga ah, taas oo lagu soo bandhigay cusbooneysiinta lixaad ee ECDC ee Qiimeynta Khatarta Degdegga ah ee COVID-19.
Maaddaama dhacdooyinka ay weli ku jiraan dalalka EU/EEA iyo qaar ka mid ah gobollada Boqortooyada Midowday, isbitaalada iyo cutubyada daryeelka xoogga badanna ay siineyaan adeegyo gobol oo gaar ah dadka isticmaala, waxaa lagugula talinayaa in macluumaadka ku saabsan cudurrada iyo sariiraha daryeelka xoogga badanna laga helo nidaamka magacaabista cutubyada gobolka ee heerarka tirakoobka 2 (NUTS-2).
Khibrada Talyaaniga iyo isbeddellada hadda jira ee dalalka kale waxay muujinayaan in masiibada COVID-19 ay si dhakhso leh ugu sii socoto EU/EEA iyo UK.
Sidaa darteed, wadamada, isbitaalada iyo cutubyada daryeelka xoogga leh waa inay isu diyaariyaan xaaladaha socda ee cudurrada bulshada ee SARS-CoV-2 iyo baahida daryeelka caafimaadka iyo daryeelka degdegga ah, gaar ahaan sida ka dhacay aagagga saameynta leh ee Talyaaniga, si ay u diyaar garoobaan tirada dadka qaba COVID-19.
Sida lagu tilmaamay qiimeynta khatarta degdegga ah ee ECDC ee dhowaan, hab deg deg ah, hore u shaqeynaya oo dhammaystiran ayaa lagama maarmaan u ah in la daahiriyo faafitaanka SARS-COV-2, iyadoo la beddelo habka la joojiyo ilaa la yareeyo, maadaama aan la fulin waqti hore, kororka degdegga ah ee la filayo ee tirada kiisaska aysan siin karin waqti ku filan go'aan qaadayaasha iyo isbitaalada si ay u fahmaan, u qaataan, u soo bandhigaan jawaabtooda.
Qiimaynta halista degdegga ah waxay sidoo kale bixisaa liis ka mid ah tallaabooyinka caafimaadka dadweynaha ee lagu yareeyo saameynta masiibada.
Waxaa jira fursad gaaban oo ay ku jirto in dalalku ay sii kordhiyaan dadaalkooda xakameynta si ay u yareeyaan xawaaraha faafitaanka SARS-CoV-2 iyo inay yareeyaan cadaadiska daryeelka caafimaadka.
Haddii aysan taasi sameynin, waxaa jira fursad ay nidaamyada daryeelka caafimaadka ee dalalka kale ee EU/EEA ay la kulmi doonaan tirada bukaanka u baahan daryeel degdeg ah maalmaha ama toddobaadyada soo socda.
Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19) oo ka dhalatay cudurka Coronavirus-CoV-2 ee loo yaqaan 'SARS Acute Respiratory Syndrome' ayaa sababay 3,000 oo qof oo ku dhintay Shiinaha iyo adduunka intiisa kale, iyo in ka badan 80,000 oo qof oo cudurka qaba, taasoo keentay masiibo aadanaha.
Sida SARS-CoV uu u eg yahay fayraska la midka ah, kaas oo sababiyay SARS kumanaan qof sanadkii 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ayaa laga yaabaa inuu ku dhaco bakaylaha isla markaana uu soo saaro calaamadaha la midka ah isla habka.
Si kastaba ha noqotee, COVID-19 waxay leedahay heerar yar oo halis ah iyo dhimashada marka loo eego SARS laakiin waxay leedahay heerar aad u badan oo cudurrada ah waxayna ku dhacdaa ragga da'da ah iyo dumarka ka badan dhalinyarada.
Iyada oo la jawaabayo daabacaadaha si dhakhso leh u kordhaya ee ku saabsan cudurrada soo baxa, maqaalkani wuxuu isku dayayaa inuu bixiyo dib u eegis waqti-dheer oo dhammaystiran oo ku saabsan mawduuca cilmi baarista ee si dhakhso leh u horumarka.
Waxaan ku dari doonnaa arrimaha aasaasiga ah ee ku saabsan cudurrada cudurka, cudurrada, fayraska, cudurrada, daaweynta, tilmaamayaasha cudurka iyo ka hortagga.
Inkastoo su'aalo badan ay weli u baahan yihiin jawaab, waxaan rajeyneynaa in dib u eegiskani uu ka caawiyo fahamka iyo baabi'inta cudurka cabsida leh.
Xuska gu'ga ee 25ka Janaayo 2020 wuxuu noqday xasuus aan la taaban karin oo aan la iloobin dhammaan dadka Shiinaha, kuwaas oo lagu sheegay inay guryahooda ku joogaan inta fasaxa socoto iyo toddobaadyo ka dib, sababtoo ah cudur cusub oo fayraska ah ayaa ka dhacay.
Fayraska wuxuu si weyn ula xiriiraa coronavirus (CoV) oo sababeysa cudurka SARS ee 2003-kii; sidaa darteed, Febraayo 11, 2020 waxaa loo magacaabay SARS-CoV-2 ee Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO) waxaana la magacaabay cudurka la xiriira COVID-19.
Cudurka ayaa ka bilaabmay Wuhan, Shiinaha, wuxuuna si dhakhso leh ugu faafay dalka oo dhan iyo in ka badan 50 dal oo adduunka ah.
Ilaa 2da Maarso 2020, waxaa jira in ka badan 80,000 oo kiis oo xaqiijin ah oo COVID-19 ah oo ay sababtay fayraska, oo in ka badan 40,000 oo bukaan ah ay ka soo kabsadeen, in ka badan 3,000 oo bukaan ahna ay dhinteen.
WHO waxay ka digtay in COVID-19 uu yahay "Cadowga ugu weyn ee dadweynaha" iyo in uu ka xoog badan yahay argagixisada.
Sida laga soo xigtay PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), in ka yar laba bilood tan iyo markii la soo saaray warbixinteeda ugu horeysa 7ka Janaayo 2020, in ka badan 200 oo maqaal oo ku saabsan COVID-19 oo ay ku jiraan fayraska, cudurrada faafa, cudurrada, cudurrada, cudurrada iyo daaweynta ayaa la daabacay oo ku tilmaamay nidaamka fayraska ee ka soo kala go'ay bukaanno badan.
Dib u eegiskani wuxuu isku dayayaa inuu soo koobo horumarka cilmi baarista ee ku saabsan mawduuc cusub oo si dhakhso leh u horumarinaya.
Mar kasta oo ay suurtagal tahay, waxaan isku dayi doonaa inaan COVID-19 la barbar dhigno SARS iyo cudur kale oo COVID-ka keena, cudurka neefsashada ee Bariga Dhexe (MERS, 2012 cudurka faafa).
Waxaan ka wada hadalnay wixii aan hadda ka ogaannay ka hortagga iyo saadaasha cudurrada iyo sidoo kale su'aalaha muhiimka ah ee weli jira.
CoVs waxaa caadi ahaan loo tixgeliyaa inay yihiin cudur aan u dhiman karin dadka, taas oo asal ahaan keentay qiyaastii 15% 4 jeer oo qabow oo caadi ah.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, qarnigii, waxaan laba jeer la kulannay cudurrada ugu badan ee cudurka loo yaqaan 'Human Bacterial CoV', kuwaas oo ah SARS-CoV iyo MERS-CoV, kuwaas oo markii ugu horreysay ka bilaabay cudurrada faafa ee Shiinaha 2003 iyo Sacuudi Carabiya 2012 siday u kala horreeyaan, waxayna si dhakhso ah ugu faafiyeen dalal kale oo ay ku jiraan cudurro iyo dhimashada daran.
Sidaa darteed, COVID-19-ka hadda jira waa cudurka COVID-19 ee saddexaad ee la diiwaangeliyo taariikhda aadanaha.
Sida lagu muujiyey sawirka 1.1, cudurrada sanbabada ee aan la garanayn ayaa markii ugu horreysay laga soo sheegay Wuhan, 31 December 2019 Guddiga Caafimaadka Qaranka ee Shiinaha.
Toddoba maalmood kadib ayaa la soo saaray taxanaha COVID.
Khasaaraha ugu horreeya ee dhimashada ee Wuhan ayaa la soo sheegay 15ka Janaayo 2020.
Dhanka kale, cudurka ayaa si dhakhso leh ugu faafay magaalooyinka, gobollada iyo waddamada hareeraheeda.
Janaayo 20, bixiyeyaasha daryeelka caafimaadka ayaa la sheegay inay qaadeen cudur, taas oo muujineysa in cudurku uu ka dhici karo dadka.
Janaayo 23, magaalada Wuhan ayaa la xiray, waxaana la joojiyay dhammaan gaadiidka dadweynaha.
Daraasaddii ugu horreysay ee cudurka lagu sameeyay 24ka Janaayo ayaa sheegtay in 21 ka mid ah 41 bukaan oo la xaqiijiyay ay si toos ah ula xiriireen suuqa Wuhan Seafood (Cuntooyinka Badda) oo loo maleynayo inay tahay meesha laga bilaabay cudurka illaa iyo hadda.
