Habab kala duwan ayaa lagu ogaadaa in fayraska uu kiciyo soo saarista walxaha caabuqa, dhallinyarada unugyada dendritic, iyo isku-darka noocyada kala duwan ee interferons (IFNs) kuwaas oo xaddidaada gudbinta fayraska iyo dardargelinta macrofase ee phagocytosis ee fayraska antigenes.
Si kastaba ha noqotee, borotiinka N ee SARS-CoV wuxuu ka caawin karaa fayraska inuu ka badbaado falcelinta nidaamka difaaca.
