Si kastaba ha noqotee, waxay u baahan yihiin 80% ka mid ah taageerada hawo-mareenka, taas oo ah wax badan oo ka badan bukaannada COVID-19 iyo waxay la socotaa heerarka ugu sarreeya ee MERS ee COVID-19.
