Qaar ka mid ah ardayda Shiinaha ayaa iskugu yimid Jaamacadda Mareykanka si ay gargaar ugu diraan meelaha uu ku dhacay cudurka Shiinaha. Iyadoo koox ka tirsan gobolka Chicago oo ku nool gobolka weyn ayaa si wadajir ah ugu diray 50,000 oo maaskaro N95 ah isbitaalada gobolka Hubei 30kii Janaayo. Ururka Gargaarka Aadanaha ee Degdegga ah ayaa la kaashanaya FedEx oo ay 200,000 maaskaro wajiga ah iyo qalab kale oo ilaalinaya gaashaanka, gaashaanka iyo qalabka kale ee gaarka loo leeyahay oo ay ku jiraan gaashaanka, ayaa loo diray Isbitaalka Wuhan Union 30kii Janaayo iyadoo loo marayo duulimaadyo degdeg ah.
"Bilo iyo Melinda Gates ayaa bishii Febraayo 5 ku dhawaaqay inay WHO ugu deeqeen $100 milyan oo lacag ah si ay u maalgeliyaan dadaallada cilmi baarista iyo daaweynta tallaalka, iyo sidoo kale si loo ilaaliyo ""dadka halista ku jira Afrika iyo Koonfurta Aasiya".
Interaction ayaa sheegtay in dawladda Shiinaha ay siisay Filibiin 200,000 oo maaskaro ah 6kii Febraayo kadib markii Senator Richard Gordon uu 3.16 milyan oo maaskaro ah u geeyay Wuhan.
