B2Anjiotensin-Enzyme Converter 2 (ACE2) waa enzymes ku xiran qanjirka sanbabada, wadnaha, kelyaha iyo qanjirka mindhicirka.
ACE2 waxay ka hortagtaa shaqada enzymes-ka beddelaya angiotensin-II ee la xiriira iyadoo la yareeyo xaddiga angiotensin-II, waxayna kordhisaa Ang1-7 waxayna ka dhigeysaa daawada bartilmaameedka ugu wanaagsan ee lagu daaweynayo cudurrada wadnaha. ACE2 waxay sidoo kale u shaqeysaa sidii meel lagu galo unugyada qaar ka mid ah coronavirus.
Nooca bini'aadamka ee enzyme-ka waxaa badanaa loo yaqaan hACE2.
Angiotensin-dejiyaha-dejiyaha 2 waa metaloenzyme zinc-ku-xiran oo ku yaal dusha sare ee unugyada endothelial iyo kuwa kale.
Protein-ka ACE2 wuxuu leeyahay domain N-terminal peptidease M2 iyo domain C-terminal colectrain renal amino acid transporter.
ACE2 waa borotiinka hal-marinta ah ee nooca I ee xubnaha xubnaha, oo booska firfircoon ee shucuurta ku shaqeeya uu ku daboolo dusha sare ee unugyada sanbabada iyo unugyada kale.
Xagga dibedda ee ACE2 waxaa ka soo saara xageeda loo yaqaan 'transmembrane domain' waxaa ka soo saara enzyme kale oo loo yaqaan 'shadeys' waxaana natiijadaas keentay in borotiinka la isku dayo uu ka soo baxo dhiigga, ugu dambeynna uu ka baxo cirbadda.
ACE2 waxay ku jirtaa xubnaha badankood: ACE2 waxay ugu weyn ku xiran tahay qanjirka unugyada ku xiran alviolus nooca II ee sambabada, enterocytes ee mindhicirka yar, unugyada ugu badan ee neerfaha iyo unugyada neerfaha iyo unugyada muruqyada qanjirka yar ee neerfaha.
Waxyaabaha ay ka muuqdaan ACE2 mRNA waxaa ka mid ah cerebral cortex, stratum, hypothylamus iyo cerebrum.
Waxqabadka koowaad ee ACE2 waa inuu u shaqeeyo sidii isbeddelka ACE.
ACE angiotensin I waxay u kala qaybiso hormoonka angiotensin II ee loo yaqaan 'vasoconscription angiotensin II'.
ACE2 waxay ka soo saarto carboxylate-terminal amino acid phenylalanine (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) oo ka soo jeedineysa angiotensin II, waxayna u haajireysaa angiotensin (1-7) oo ah vasodilator (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 waxay kala saari kartaa dhowr peptide oo kale, oo ay ku jiraan [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dinerphine A iyo ghrelin.
ACE2 waxay xakameysaa isweydaarsiga qanjirka ee xamuulka amino acid SLC6A19 waxayna la xiriirtaa cudurka wadnaha.
ACE2 oo ah borotiinka taransaamerinka ayaa u adeegaya sidii xarunta ugu weyn ee lagu galo unugyada qaar ka mid ah coronavirus-yada, oo ay ku jiraan HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (viruska masuulka ka ah SARS); iyo SARS-CoV-2 (viruska masuulka ka ah COVID-19).
Si gaar ah, waxaa lagu sheegay in xidhiidhka SARS-CoV iyo SARS-CoV2 ee ku jira borotiinka S1 ee ku jira domainka enzymatic ee ACE2 uu ku dhiso dusha unugyada, taas oo keentay in endocytosis iyo fayrasyada iyo enzymes-ka labadaba ay u wareegaan endosomes-ka u dhexeeya unugyada.
Nidaamkan gelitaanka wuxuu sidoo kale u baahan yahay in loo qoro borotiinka S ee loo yaqaan 'host serine protease TMPRSS2', oo ka hortaggeedu yahay daaweyn suurtagal ah oo hadda la baaro. Tani waxay ka caawisay dhowr qof inay qiyaasaan in yareynta heerarka ACE2 ee unugyada ay ka caawin karto la dagaalanka caabuqa.
