Macluumaad yar ayaa la heli karaa oo ku saabsan cudurka COVID-19 iyo dhaawaca microscopic.
Macluumaadka ugu muhiimsan ee cudurka cudurka ee baaritaanka mindhicirka waa:
Macroscopy: Puricary, pericarditis, lung consolidation (qabashada biyaha sanbabada) iyo cudurka sanbabada
Waxaa jira afar nooc oo cudurka 'viral pneumonia':
Nuxurka 'Light pneumonia': Dhibcaha cudurka 'pulmonary edema', 'pneumocyte hyperplasia', 'large atypical pneumocytes', 'limphocytic infiltration', iyo 'multinucleated' oo ka kooban caabuqyo badan oo ku dhaca unugyada.
Cudurka Pneumonia: Cudurka loo yaqaan 'Damaged Drifted Alviolare', oo ay ku jiraan waxyeelooyinka ka soo baxa alviolare.
