Daawo:Cod-dhimista cudurka ayaa ah mid aad u badan oo ku saleysan habdhaqanka cudurka ee kale, laakiin kiisaskaas ayaa laga soo warramay in ay ka soo kabsadeen COVID-19 kadib natiijooyinka baaritaanka COVID-19 ee la helay.
