Ma jiro daawo ama tallaal loo oggol yahay in lagu daaweeyo cudurka.
Cilmi-baarista caalamiga ah ee tallaallada iyo daawooyinka COVID-19 waxaa sameynaya hay'adaha dowladda, kooxaha aqoonyahanka ah iyo cilmi baarayaasha warshadaha.
Bishii Maarso, WHO waxay bilawday tijaabooyin taageero isugu jira si loo qiimeeyo saameynta daaweynta afar ka mid ah isku-darka antiviral ee hadda jira ee ugu ballanqaadka badan waxtarka.
Ma jiro tallaal, laakiin shirkado badan ayaa si firfircoon u soo saara tartamada tallaalka.
Shaqooyinkii hore ee lagu sameeyay SARS-CoV ayaa la isticmaalaa sababtoo ah labadaba SARS-CoV iyo SARS-CoV-2 waxay isticmaalaan macaamiisha ACE2 si ay u galaan unugyada aadanaha.
Saddex istiraatiijiyad oo tallaal ah ayaa la baaray.
Marka hore, cilmi baarayaashu waxay rabaan inay sameeyaan tallaal fayras oo dhan.
U adeegsiga fayraska, ha ahaato mid dhintay ama aan shaqeyn, waxaa loogu talagalay in la sameeyo falcelin degdeg ah oo ka hortag ah oo ka imanaya cudurka COVID-19.
Farsamada labaad, waa tallaalka subunit, oo lagu doonayo in la sameeyo tallaal ka dhigaya in nidaamka difaaca ee fayraska uu dareemo.
Xaaladda SARS-CoV-2, daraasaddan ayaa lagu ogaaday in ay tahay borotiinka S-spike ee caawiya fayraska inuu galo ACE2 enzyme.
Farsamada saddexaad waa tallaalka nucleic acid (DNA ama RNA, farsamooyinka cusub ee loo sameeyo tallaalka).
Si loo ilaaliyo badbaadada iyo waxtarka, tallaallada tijaabada ah waa inay ka tijaabiyaan mid ka mid ah farsamooyinkaas. 16 Maarso 2020, tijaabada ugu horreysa ee tallaalka oo ay ku jiraan afar mutadawiciin ayaa ka bilaabatay Seattle.
Fayraska ayaa ku jira fayraska oo aan waxyeello ka geysan karin fayraska. Kororka ku tiirsan antibody-ka ayaa lagu tilmaamay inay tahay caqabad suurtagal ah oo lagu horumarinayo tallaalka SARS-COV-2, laakiin waa mid muran leh.
In ka badan 300 tijaabooyin oo firfircoon ayaa la sameeyay tan iyo Abriil 2020.
Toddoba tijaabo ayaa lagu qiimeeyay daaweynta horey loo oggolaaday daaweynta cudurka Malaria, oo ay ku jiraan afar daraasadood oo ka sarreeya Hydroxychloroquine ama Chloroquine.
Inta badan daraasadaha Shiinaha ayaa loo sameeyaa in daawooyinka antiviral loo isticmaalo ujeedooyin kala duwan, waxaana laga filayaa in sagaal tijaabo oo wajiga III ah oo ku saabsan Remdesivir laga soo warbixiyo dalal kala duwan dhammaadka Abriil.
Dib u eegis dhaqameed oo ku saabsan horumarka la xiriira tallaallada COVID-19 iyo kuwa u tartamaya daawada ayaa la sameeyay bishii Abriil 2020. Qaar ka mid ah daawooyinka antiviral ee hadda jira ee lagu daaweynayo COVID-19 ayaa la qiimeynayaa oo ay ku jiraan Remdesivir, Chlorokine iyo Hydroxychloroquine, Lopinavir / Retonovir iyo Interferon Bitter.
Tijaabada tijaabada ah ee waxtarka waxaa leh Remdesivir bishii Maarso 2020.
Horumarinta tirada bukaanka ee la daaweeyey iyadoo la adeegsanayo daawooyinka tijaabada ah ee Remdesivir ayaa la arkay.
Tijaabooyinka cudurka ee wajiga III ayaa lagu qabtaa Mareykanka, Shiinaha iyo Talyaaniga. Chlorokine, oo horey loogu isticmaalay daaweynta makaraayadda, ayaa lagu daraaseeyay Shiinaha bishii Febraayo 2020 natiijooyin bilow ah.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, waa in dib loo eegaa tiirarka cilmi baarista.
Maamulka caafimaadka ee Kuuriya iyo Shiinaha ayaa ku talinaya isticmaalka chloroquine.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, Machadka Virology ee Wuhan, marka ay soo jeediso qiyaasta hal tuug ee daawada maalin kasta, waxay ogaatay in qiyaastaas labanlaabtu ay noqon karto mid aad u khatar badan oo dhimasho badan.
Bishii Maarso 28, 2020, FDA waxay oggolaatay isticmaalka degdegga ah ee Hydroxychloroquine iyo Chloroquine iyadoo la tixgelinayo dhakhaatiirta daryeela dadka qaba COVID-19. Tilmaamaha Shiinaha ee 7aad ee daabacaadda ayaa sidoo kale ku daray interferon, raibbavirin ama umfenovir marka la eego COVID-19.
Xogta bilowga ah waxay muujineysaa in qiyaaso sare oo rabaybavirin ah loo baahan yahay si looga hortago SARS-CoV-2 vitro.
Nitasoxanoid ayaa lagu talinayaa in lagu sameeyo daraasado dheeraad ah oo Vivo ah kadib markii la muujiyey in la joojiyay heerarka hoose ee SARS-CoV-2. Daraasadaha ayaa cadeeyay in diyaarinta borotiinka ugu horreeya ee spike-ka ah ee loo yaqaan 'transmembrane protease serine 2' (TMPRSS2) ay lagama maarmaan tahay in SARS-CoV-2 uu galo iyada oo la adeegsanayo falcelin la leh ACE2 receptor.
Daraasadaha loo yaqaan 'Chloroquine' iyo 'Hydroxychloroquine' oo ay ku jiraan ama aan lahayn azithromycin ayaa leh xaddidaad culus oo ka hortagtay in bulshada caafimaadka ay qaataan daaweyntaas iyada oo aan la baran.
Dhibaatada cytokine waxay noqon kartaa xaalad adag marka COVID-19-ka daran uu soo baxo.
Waxaa jira caddayn muujinaya in hydroxychloroquine uu leeyahay awoodda si loo xakameeyo sii deynta si dhakhso ah ee cytokine.
Waxay ku socotaa tallaabo heer qaran ah oo ah marxaladda 2 ee tijaabada aan kala sooc lahayn ee Talyaaniga ka dib markii ay aragtay natiijooyin wanaagsan dadka qaba cudurrada daran.
Tijaabada dhiigga oo lagu daro serum feritine si loo aqoonsado masiibada cytokine waxay ka dhigan tahay ka hortagga kororka cudurka, kaas oo la rumeysan yahay inuu keeno dhimashada dadka qaba cudurka.
2017 CAR T cell therapy waxaa ansixiyay FDA iyada oo loo marayo daraasadaha kiisaska la xiriira hore ee lagu daaweeyo cudurka cytokine-release syndrome ee steroid-refractory induced by a separate factor.
Ilaa hadda, ma jirto wax caddayn ah oo aan joogto ahayn oo la xakameyn karo oo muujinaya in Tocilizumab uu yahay daaweyn waxtar leh oo loogu talagalay CRS.
Dadka ka bogsaday COVID-19 waxaa la raadinayaa inay noqdaan hab aan tallaal lahayn oo loo tallaalo oo loo siiyo antibodies-ka la soo saaray ee nidaamka difaaca jirka iyo kuwa la soo saaray ee la siiyaa kuwa u baahan.
Hababkaasi ayaa lagu tijaabiyey SARS natiijooyin aan la hubin.
Baareynta fayraska waa habka la filayo ee habka gaarka ah ee daaweynta antibody-ka aan shaqeyn karin ay ku dhexdhexaadineyso difaaca SARS-CoV-2.
Si kastaba ha noqotee, habab kale sida cytotoxicity-ka unugyada ku tiirsan antibody iyo / ama phagocytosis ayaa suurtagal noqon kara.
Noocyada kale ee daaweynta antibody-ka aan shaqeyn karin, tusaale ahaan, isticmaalka monoclonal antibody-ka soo saaray, ayaa horumarsan.
Wax soo saarka serum-ka Convalescent, oo ka kooban dareeraha dhiigga ee laga soo qaatay bukaannada la soo kabsaday, ayaa la kordhin karaa si loo soo saaro antibodies gaar ah oo si dhakhso leh loo soo saaro fayraska.
